BT /F2 22 Tf 50.00 783.89 Td (TuneUp Application Report) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50.00 738.89 Td (Project: TuneUp) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50.00 720.89 Td (Type: Final-Year Dissertation Mobile App) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50.00 702.89 Td (Platform: React Native / Expo mobile app with FastAPI backend) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50.00 684.89 Td (Author: Yavuz Sever) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50.00 666.89 Td (Repository: TuneUp-Shut-the-SOUND-up-) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50.00 648.89 Td (Date: 5 May 2026) Tj ET
BT /F2 15 Tf 50.00 615.89 Td (1. Executive Summary) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50.00 582.89 Td (TuneUp is a mobile music practice assistant that combines real-time instrument tuning,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50.00 566.89 Td (AI-assisted song analysis, song library management, guided lessons, and Song Flow practice in one) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50.00 550.89 Td (full-stack prototype. The app is inspired by the learning flow of products such as Rocksmith and) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50.00 534.89 Td (Yousician, but it uses its own original design, data structures, code, and demo content.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50.00 507.89 Td (The project focuses on building a practical dissertation-ready prototype rather than a static) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50.00 491.89 Td (concept. It includes a React Native / Expo frontend, a FastAPI backend, Supabase integration,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50.00 475.89 Td (native microphone handling, local song persistence, asynchronous audio analysis jobs, and a) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50.00 459.89 Td (polished dark/glass visual design.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50.00 432.89 Td (TuneUp is deliberately honest about AI-generated music content. Generated chord charts and tabs) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50.00 416.89 Td (are treated as AI Drafts, not verified official tabs. Users review confidence values, warnings,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50.00 400.89 Td (tuning metadata, chord counts, tab counts, and BPM before saving or practising a generated chart.) Tj ET
BT /F2 15 Tf 50.00 365.89 Td (2. Project Aim and Motivation) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50.00 332.89 Td (The aim of TuneUp is to support musicians as they move from preparation to practice:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50.00 305.89 Td (- Tune the instrument.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50.00 288.89 Td (- Learn technique and theory.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50.00 271.89 Td (- Upload or import a song.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50.00 254.89 Td (- Convert audio into a playable draft chart.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50.00 237.89 Td (- Review and save the chart.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50.00 220.89 Td (- Practise through Song Flow.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50.00 203.89 Td (- Track progress through XP, streaks, badges, and profile shelves.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50.00 179.89 Td (Many beginner and intermediate musicians use separate tools for tuning, tabs, lessons, and) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50.00 163.89 Td (practice tracking. TuneUp explores whether these workflows can be combined into a single) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 50.00 147.89 Td (mobile-first learning assistant with a consistent user experience.) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50.00 120.89 Td (The project also investigates real implementation constraints: native audio input, mobile) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50.00 104.89 Td (permissions, asynchronous backend processing, Supabase storage, manifest validation, unreliable) Tj ET
BT /F2 10 Tf 50.00 88.89 Td (AI transcription, and local demo reliability for a dissertation viva.) Tj ET
endstream
